    <section class="header-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h1>What is an E-Invoice?</h1>
                <p class="lead">
                    E-Invoicing is the electronic generation and exchange of invoices between buyers and sellers in a
                    standardized digital format. It streamlines invoicing processes, reduces paperwork, and improves
                    accuracy.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why E-Invoicing Matters Section -->
