                        E-Invoicing transforms the traditional invoicing process by replacing paper-based invoices with
                        a digital alternative that can be processed faster, more accurately, and with greater
                        transparency.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How E-Invoicing Works Section -->
     <section class="how-it-works-section py-5 bg-light text-center"></section>
